1
00:00:06,645 --> 00:00:09,290
Lin Chong... He will be killed.

2
00:00:09,290 --> 00:00:12,770
What have you done
aside from craft impractical theories?

3
00:00:12,770 --> 00:00:14,850
It's all talk, no action.

4
00:00:14,850 --> 00:00:17,270
One must not destroy the country
in the process.

5
00:00:17,270 --> 00:00:20,750
We shall rebuild this nation
from the shadows.

6
00:00:20,750 --> 00:00:22,270
We cannot even give him a grave?

7
00:00:22,270 --> 00:00:23,980
You need not know any more.

8
00:00:23,980 --> 00:00:25,900
I know. You will become my attendant.

9
00:00:25,900 --> 00:00:29,600
Salt makes this world go round.

10
00:00:29,600 --> 00:00:31,980
Salt is the embodiment of money.

11
00:00:31,980 --> 00:00:36,070
You will need to overcome death's limits.

12
00:00:36,070 --> 00:00:39,730
I do not wish to associate
with Liangshan Marsh.

13
00:00:39,730 --> 00:00:42,265
When two surprising elements merge together,

14
00:00:42,265 --> 00:00:45,185
they bring about unprecedented change.

15
00:00:45,850 --> 00:00:48,620
I promise to return with him.

16
00:01:09,025 --> 00:01:10,320
Lin Chong!

17
00:01:10,320 --> 00:01:13,420
What? What seems to be the issue?

18
00:01:15,355 --> 00:01:16,700
[Song Jiang, Yuncheng Clerk]

19
00:01:16,700 --> 00:01:18,590
I wonder.

20
00:01:52,695 --> 00:01:56,600
[Lin Chong, Former Spearman Instructor]

21
00:01:56,600 --> 00:02:01,770
I am one who shares Song Jiang's ambitions.
[Chao Gai, Bandit King]

22
00:02:01,770 --> 00:02:04,540
It's an honor to meet you, Chao Gai.

23
00:02:04,540 --> 00:02:06,900
[Episode 3]

24
00:02:06,900 --> 00:02:10,020
Song Jiang did not evacuate from Yuncheng.

25
00:02:10,020 --> 00:02:13,655
He said he could not preach a great cause

26
00:02:13,655 --> 00:02:16,904
if he did not even trust his own men.

27
00:02:16,904 --> 00:02:18,934
That does not surprise me.

28
00:02:24,030 --> 00:02:28,120
There is something I must tell you.

29
00:02:29,415 --> 00:02:34,020
Gao Qiu is but a foolish man

30
00:02:34,020 --> 00:02:36,900
who only knows to play ball.

31
00:02:36,900 --> 00:02:39,355
The one manipulating his strings,

32
00:02:39,355 --> 00:02:40,920
is a man named Li Fu.

33
00:02:40,920 --> 00:02:42,300
[Enforcing the Way in Heaven's Name]

34
00:02:42,300 --> 00:02:45,290
<i>Li Fu? That is a name I do not know.</i>

35
00:02:45,290 --> 00:02:47,599
<i>Is he with the Imperial Guard?</i>

36
00:02:47,599 --> 00:02:49,069
No.

37
00:02:49,725 --> 00:02:52,730
He is merely another civil official.
[Lu Zhi Shen, Monk]

38
00:02:52,730 --> 00:02:56,440
Yet he did not flinch in Gao Qiu's presence.

39
00:02:56,440 --> 00:03:01,600
He was especially curious about you,
and Song Jiang's writings.

40
00:03:01,600 --> 00:03:03,770
How much does this Li Fu know?
[Ruan Xiao Wu, Fisherman]

41
00:03:03,770 --> 00:03:05,085
[Wu Yong, Private Tutor]

42
00:03:05,085 --> 00:03:06,935
I am not sure.

43
00:03:09,705 --> 00:03:13,400
Now, what is my next mission?

44
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:21,314
Lin Chong, you will be escorted
to the Cangzhou prison as intended.

45
00:03:21,314 --> 00:03:22,799
Why?

46
00:03:22,799 --> 00:03:25,277
To seize the stronghold at Liangshan Marsh.

47
00:03:25,277 --> 00:03:27,230
But this will come in due time.

48
00:03:27,230 --> 00:03:34,132
You must first find the doctor, An Dao Quan,

49
00:03:34,132 --> 00:03:35,987
who is currently held in Cangzhou.

50
00:03:35,987 --> 00:03:39,303
I do not see the connection between the two.

51
00:03:39,303 --> 00:03:43,525
The wife of the individual
who is our key to Liangshan Marsh,

52
00:03:43,525 --> 00:03:45,910
is afflicted with a serious illness.

53
00:03:45,910 --> 00:03:48,940
Only An Dao Quan can cure her.

54
00:03:50,722 --> 00:03:52,532
I understand.

55
00:03:53,530 --> 00:03:55,760
It is a welcome challenge.

56
00:03:57,257 --> 00:03:58,817
Are you certain?

57
00:04:02,415 --> 00:04:06,690
Before I go, I must ask a favor.

58
00:04:06,690 --> 00:04:08,170
Ask away, old friend.

59
00:04:11,710 --> 00:04:15,000
Please deliver this to Song Jiang.

60
00:04:16,570 --> 00:04:18,910
Is there anything you wish to tell him?

61
00:04:22,790 --> 00:04:24,700
Tell him...

62
00:04:27,080 --> 00:04:29,040
"Lin Chong is alive".

63
00:04:36,875 --> 00:04:39,685
Listen well, foolish guards.

64
00:04:40,675 --> 00:04:45,650
You two will escort this man to Cangzhou.

65
00:04:45,650 --> 00:04:47,950
When asked where your squad has gone,

66
00:04:47,950 --> 00:04:49,770
this shall be your answer.

67
00:04:49,770 --> 00:04:52,465
"We were ambushed by bandits."

68
00:04:52,465 --> 00:04:58,895
"Though we do not know their intentions,
our squad fought valiantly."

69
00:04:59,620 --> 00:05:02,000
Now repeat.

70
00:05:04,665 --> 00:05:06,520
Do not cower!

71
00:05:06,520 --> 00:05:08,420
They will realize your lies.

72
00:05:09,385 --> 00:05:13,020
We... We were ambushed by bandits.

73
00:05:13,020 --> 00:05:15,135
- Our squad...
- Wrong!

74
00:05:15,135 --> 00:05:17,401
"Though we do not know their intentions".

75
00:05:17,401 --> 00:05:20,683
Repeat this as you march.

76
00:05:21,576 --> 00:05:23,756
We will be watching.

77
00:05:24,455 --> 00:05:28,770
Harm Lin Chong, and you will see hell.

78
00:05:28,770 --> 00:05:30,460
You hear me?

79
00:05:39,925 --> 00:05:41,850
Chao Gai!

80
00:05:41,850 --> 00:05:43,335
What is your report?

81
00:05:43,335 --> 00:05:49,150
Lin Chong is headed to Cangzhou.
I guarantee his safe journey.

82
00:05:49,150 --> 00:05:50,405
Thank you.

83
00:05:50,405 --> 00:05:52,227
Song Jiang.

84
00:05:52,227 --> 00:05:55,650
Lin Chong requested
I deliver his prisoner tag to you.

85
00:05:55,650 --> 00:05:58,600
[Lin Chong]

86
00:05:58,600 --> 00:06:04,170
I also have a message from him.
He says, "Lin Chong is alive".

87
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:32,630
My son grows more endearing by the day.
[Shi Li, Chief of Shi Family Village]

88
00:06:34,620 --> 00:06:39,840
All children one day leave the nest.
[Madam Wang, Wang Jin's mother]

89
00:06:41,027 --> 00:06:47,597
Yet my own selfishness prays
he will stay a moment longer.

90
00:06:53,690 --> 00:06:56,620
[Shi Jin, Shi Li's son]

91
00:06:57,615 --> 00:06:59,870
Stand, Shi Jin.

92
00:06:59,870 --> 00:07:01,465
[Wang Jin, Former Martial Arts Instructor]

93
00:07:01,465 --> 00:07:04,405
The dragons on your back
are at death's door,

94
00:07:05,060 --> 00:07:07,380
Shi Jin, the Nine Tattooed Dragons.

95
00:07:11,135 --> 00:07:15,860
My son can only converse through combat.

96
00:07:15,860 --> 00:07:21,250
He is happy to have found
a fellow fighting spirit.

97
00:07:24,195 --> 00:07:27,580
"We were ambushed by bandits."

98
00:07:27,580 --> 00:07:29,900
"Though we do not know their intentions,"

99
00:07:29,900 --> 00:07:33,830
"our squad..."

100
00:07:33,830 --> 00:07:37,250
"they fought valiantly."

101
00:07:37,250 --> 00:07:40,410
"We were ambushed by bandits."

102
00:07:40,410 --> 00:07:43,440
[Cangzhou Prison]

103
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:48,030
Only two escorts?
Where is the rest of your squad?

104
00:07:48,030 --> 00:07:50,622
Your captain is nowhere to be seen.

105
00:07:50,622 --> 00:07:53,857
We were ambushed by bandits.

106
00:07:53,857 --> 00:07:56,417
Though we do not know their intentions...

107
00:07:58,730 --> 00:08:01,290
- Our squad...
- Enough. Go.

108
00:08:14,375 --> 00:08:18,080
Lin Chong was safely escorted to prison?

109
00:08:18,080 --> 00:08:21,715
I ordered his death!
[Gao Qiu, General of the Imperial Guard]

110
00:08:21,715 --> 00:08:26,324
The squad was ambushed by bandits,
and valiantly drove them away...

111
00:08:27,650 --> 00:08:30,160
"Valiantly"? What rubbish.

112
00:08:32,139 --> 00:08:34,119
No matter.

113
00:08:35,020 --> 00:08:41,580
Jailed prisoners die often,
for one reason or another.

114
00:08:42,385 --> 00:08:44,860
Send in our best men.

115
00:08:44,860 --> 00:08:46,330
Yes, sir.

116
00:08:49,745 --> 00:08:51,690
You have returned.

117
00:08:51,690 --> 00:08:55,618
Commander Wang He, reporting.

118
00:08:55,618 --> 00:09:00,570
I hear Gao Qiu raised quite a commotion?
[Li Fu, Qinglian Temple]

119
00:09:00,570 --> 00:09:05,150
Yes, sir. He failed to assassinate Lin Chong.

120
00:09:05,150 --> 00:09:09,060
I see. Lin Chong stands out.

121
00:09:09,060 --> 00:09:14,085
Let him roam. See where he lands.

122
00:09:14,085 --> 00:09:17,195
Gao Qiu has already sent his men to Cangzhou.

123
00:09:18,658 --> 00:09:23,480
Gao Qiu has failed once before.

124
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:25,730
He will not succeed by repeating his methods.

125
00:09:25,730 --> 00:09:28,610
And the smuggled salt?

126
00:09:28,610 --> 00:09:34,516
We have yet to discover its origins, sir.
[Wang He, Commander of the Qinglian Spies]

127
00:09:34,516 --> 00:09:36,396
Is that so.

128
00:09:38,625 --> 00:09:42,780
How goes this search?

129
00:09:42,780 --> 00:09:46,440
We are capturing wanted bandits,
but none lead to their ensemble.

130
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:50,660
However, there have been witness reports,

131
00:09:51,810 --> 00:09:55,040
here, here,

132
00:09:55,990 --> 00:09:59,840
here, and here...

133
00:10:01,035 --> 00:10:04,310
Of this hulking monk.

134
00:10:04,310 --> 00:10:07,695
The man known both by Lin Chong,
and Wang Jin.

135
00:10:07,695 --> 00:10:09,075
Yes, sir.

136
00:10:17,545 --> 00:10:20,860
Perhaps our search was misguided.

137
00:10:20,860 --> 00:10:22,180
Pardon?

138
00:10:27,995 --> 00:10:32,730
<i>We only assumed
this was written by a bandit.</i>

139
00:10:32,730 --> 00:10:34,840
<i>In other words?</i>

140
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:41,290
<i>Like the moon, hidden while the sun rises,</i>

141
00:10:42,270 --> 00:10:45,620
perhaps he is a man invisible to our eyes.

142
00:10:47,810 --> 00:10:52,830
Search not only the dark depths,
but the sunlit paths as well.

143
00:10:55,495 --> 00:10:57,000
Am I clear?

144
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:58,290
Yes, sir.

145
00:11:00,665 --> 00:11:03,730
Pagoda-Shifting Heavenly King!

146
00:11:03,730 --> 00:11:05,590
Charge!

147
00:11:05,590 --> 00:11:09,560
Perhaps we ought to deploy an envoy

148
00:11:09,560 --> 00:11:11,900
as Sir Yuan Ming suggested.

149
00:11:11,900 --> 00:11:17,230
Our militia only bother to demand bribes
from local officials.

150
00:11:17,230 --> 00:11:18,395
They will investigate nothing.

151
00:11:18,395 --> 00:11:20,980
I cannot have that.

152
00:11:20,980 --> 00:11:23,125
We have objectives to fulfill.

153
00:11:23,125 --> 00:11:27,945
Is there no honorable man within our forces?

154
00:11:27,945 --> 00:11:30,200
Perhaps Yang Zhi, of the Imperial Guard.

155
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:34,650
Interesting. Tell me about this Yang Zhi.

156
00:11:35,745 --> 00:11:38,520
<i>He is a man who holds pride in his lineage,</i>

157
00:11:38,520 --> 00:11:40,545
<i>being a descendant of the hero, Yang Ye.</i>

158
00:11:40,545 --> 00:11:44,525
<i>He is a skilled warrior,
who wouldn't dare betray the nation.</i>

159
00:11:45,580 --> 00:11:47,440
Fire!

160
00:12:00,025 --> 00:12:02,070
[Yang Zhi, Imperial Guard]

161
00:12:02,070 --> 00:12:04,060
Focus your aim!

162
00:12:04,060 --> 00:12:08,915
Yang Zhi, the Blue-faced Beast.

163
00:12:08,915 --> 00:12:13,355
A legendary name
that will be spoken of for ages.

164
00:12:16,310 --> 00:12:18,250
Now that is a good tale.

165
00:12:30,665 --> 00:12:32,750
Yang Zhi.

166
00:12:32,750 --> 00:12:36,339
- Yes, sir?
- May I have a moment?

167
00:12:36,339 --> 00:12:41,675
A brief one, sir. I am busy,
as I have been appointed to be an envoy.

168
00:12:41,675 --> 00:12:46,945
I am the one who recommended you
to General Gao Qiu.

169
00:12:47,610 --> 00:12:49,080
Pardon?

170
00:12:50,820 --> 00:12:53,080
Yang Zhi.

171
00:12:56,810 --> 00:12:59,410
I will bestow a special mission onto you.

172
00:13:02,407 --> 00:13:08,560
Amend your ways
when you have realized your mistake.

173
00:13:08,560 --> 00:13:10,415
Yes, ma'am.

174
00:13:10,415 --> 00:13:13,435
[Know your mistakes, and correct them]

175
00:13:15,165 --> 00:13:20,150
You must concentrate till the last stroke.

176
00:13:20,150 --> 00:13:21,580
Yes, ma'am.

177
00:13:33,595 --> 00:13:36,690
What? Is that all?

178
00:13:36,690 --> 00:13:38,345
Not at all.

179
00:13:38,345 --> 00:13:42,815
This is nothing
compared to your mother's lessons.

180
00:13:44,940 --> 00:13:47,620
I struggled with her teachings as well.

181
00:13:49,045 --> 00:13:51,610
Master Wang Jin! Bandits!

182
00:13:51,610 --> 00:13:53,335
Bandits have arrived!

183
00:13:53,335 --> 00:13:55,075
Bandits?

184
00:13:56,712 --> 00:14:00,412
Shi Jin, this is another lesson.

185
00:14:01,270 --> 00:14:02,760
Yes, Master.

186
00:14:14,665 --> 00:14:18,350
Shi Jin, the Nine Tattooed Dragons!

187
00:14:18,350 --> 00:14:20,425
You face us alone?

188
00:14:20,425 --> 00:14:23,855
Has your village finally abandoned you?

189
00:14:24,845 --> 00:14:28,850
I will strike your tattooed body,

190
00:14:28,850 --> 00:14:34,200
till your nine dragons
are beaten beyond recognition!

191
00:14:53,215 --> 00:14:56,770
[Cangzhou]

192
00:14:56,770 --> 00:14:58,270
Bai Sheng, bring a support.

193
00:14:58,270 --> 00:15:00,020
- Yes, sir.
- No crying.

194
00:15:00,020 --> 00:15:02,480
- Next.
- There's been another cave-in.

195
00:15:02,480 --> 00:15:04,980
Ready yourself, An Dao Quan.

196
00:15:04,980 --> 00:15:06,900
The labor here is too grueling.

197
00:15:06,900 --> 00:15:09,650
They're practically working us to death.

198
00:15:09,650 --> 00:15:11,580
Lie down.

199
00:15:12,535 --> 00:15:14,280
- The support.
- You patch him, Bai Sheng.

200
00:15:14,280 --> 00:15:16,615
- What?
- Show me your injury.

201
00:15:16,615 --> 00:15:19,782
Yes, I will sew you up later.

202
00:15:19,782 --> 00:15:22,132
Use this rag to stop the bleeding.

203
00:15:23,285 --> 00:15:25,330
Let me see him.

204
00:15:25,330 --> 00:15:30,200
Here, he won't stop making a fuss.
It's nothing serious.

205
00:15:30,200 --> 00:15:32,995
[An Dao Quan, Prisoner, Doctor]

206
00:15:32,995 --> 00:15:34,650
- Are you in pain?
- No.

207
00:15:34,650 --> 00:15:37,910
It did at first, but not at all now.

208
00:15:37,910 --> 00:15:39,610
I see.

209
00:15:39,610 --> 00:15:42,190
There's no hope for this one.

210
00:15:42,190 --> 00:15:43,490
- Next.
- What?

211
00:15:43,490 --> 00:15:46,700
How so? He's perked up.
[Bai Sheng, Prisoner, Thief]

212
00:15:46,700 --> 00:15:48,065
- Don't ignore me!
- Move.

213
00:15:48,065 --> 00:15:50,445
Out of the way.

214
00:15:51,326 --> 00:15:55,060
He will lose his life
once I've fixed this man.

215
00:15:55,060 --> 00:15:56,900
Ridiculous.

216
00:15:56,900 --> 00:15:58,110
Take this.

217
00:15:58,110 --> 00:16:00,020
Use this ointment,
it will mend in a few days.

218
00:16:00,020 --> 00:16:02,085
Next. Out of the way.

219
00:16:02,085 --> 00:16:03,787
You, wake up.

220
00:16:04,770 --> 00:16:06,410
Open your mouth.

221
00:16:07,615 --> 00:16:09,660
Your eyes, too.

222
00:16:09,660 --> 00:16:12,580
- Hey!
- He is already dead.

223
00:16:16,625 --> 00:16:18,020
Why?

224
00:16:18,020 --> 00:16:19,560
He said he felt no pain.

225
00:16:19,560 --> 00:16:21,925
Pain is what keeps us alive.

226
00:16:21,925 --> 00:16:25,095
- Alright, lie down.
- Doctor, we got an emergency!

227
00:16:25,095 --> 00:16:27,285
Get him up here.

228
00:16:28,360 --> 00:16:29,790
Lie down.

229
00:16:32,665 --> 00:16:34,270
Toss him out once he's dead.

230
00:16:34,270 --> 00:16:36,250
I won't kill the man.

231
00:16:45,335 --> 00:16:48,600
- Bai Sheng, boil the water.
- Yes, sir.

232
00:16:48,600 --> 00:16:51,750
So, what is this?

233
00:16:51,750 --> 00:16:55,940
Can you not tell? I was stabbed.

234
00:16:55,940 --> 00:16:58,045
Stabbed?

235
00:16:58,045 --> 00:17:00,679
This was clearly self-inflicted.

236
00:17:00,679 --> 00:17:03,199
Why do something so foolish?

237
00:17:04,527 --> 00:17:06,877
To come see you.

238
00:17:10,245 --> 00:17:12,030
An Dao Quan.

239
00:17:12,030 --> 00:17:14,730
To come see me?

240
00:17:14,730 --> 00:17:16,190
What if you die?

241
00:17:16,190 --> 00:17:18,110
You're a master doctor.

242
00:17:18,110 --> 00:17:22,295
And since you only entertain your patients,

243
00:17:22,295 --> 00:17:24,645
I turned myself into one.

244
00:17:26,035 --> 00:17:27,160
Why?

245
00:17:27,160 --> 00:17:29,530
To help you escape.

246
00:17:29,530 --> 00:17:30,870
Dead men and their lies.

247
00:17:30,870 --> 00:17:32,365
I am no liar.

248
00:17:32,365 --> 00:17:35,745
I have my patients. I will not leave.

249
00:17:35,745 --> 00:17:36,904
Wait.

250
00:17:36,904 --> 00:17:42,008
You are fated to save something bigger.

251
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:50,080
You must save this very country.

252
00:17:55,980 --> 00:17:57,620
- Wait!
- Hey!

253
00:18:06,560 --> 00:18:10,250
[Ma Gui, Song Jiang's spy]

254
00:18:12,700 --> 00:18:14,820
What are you doing?

255
00:18:16,005 --> 00:18:17,470
You there!

256
00:18:17,470 --> 00:18:19,210
Please, run!

257
00:18:34,323 --> 00:18:37,310
Gao Lian, Follow her.

258
00:18:37,310 --> 00:18:39,160
Yes, sir.
[Gao Lian, Qinglian Spy]

259
00:18:55,225 --> 00:18:57,040
I shall lend a hand.

260
00:18:57,040 --> 00:18:58,775
Sir, we could never...

261
00:18:58,775 --> 00:19:01,675
Please, I only wish to help.

262
00:19:04,985 --> 00:19:07,600
I shall lift this side.

263
00:19:07,600 --> 00:19:09,342
- Ready?
- Yes, sir.

264
00:19:10,396 --> 00:19:12,486
Ready, and...

265
00:19:15,575 --> 00:19:16,870
This won't do...

266
00:19:16,870 --> 00:19:18,975
It seems you all are struggling.

267
00:19:25,606 --> 00:19:28,376
Is it so unusual to see an envoy around?

268
00:19:29,350 --> 00:19:31,010
No, sir.

269
00:19:32,835 --> 00:19:34,690
Allow me to lend a hand.

270
00:19:34,690 --> 00:19:36,420
- Men, go assist them.
- What?

271
00:19:41,555 --> 00:19:43,450
- Ready?
- Yes, sir.

272
00:19:43,450 --> 00:19:45,000
Now lift.

273
00:19:50,915 --> 00:19:53,020
That should do it.

274
00:19:53,020 --> 00:19:56,580
Thank you, sirs. I am in your debt.

275
00:19:58,295 --> 00:19:59,540
- Thank you.
- Take care.

276
00:19:59,540 --> 00:20:02,170
- Thank you.
- Safe travels.

277
00:20:04,200 --> 00:20:08,040
Pardon me, but I must hurry along.

278
00:20:09,940 --> 00:20:11,450
Wait.

279
00:20:13,700 --> 00:20:15,600
Yes, sir?

280
00:20:16,816 --> 00:20:20,246
I have never seen
an official assist a peddler.

281
00:20:22,030 --> 00:20:23,540
What is your name?

282
00:20:24,705 --> 00:20:26,610
I apologize for the lack of introductions.

283
00:20:26,610 --> 00:20:31,566
My name is Song Jiang. I am a local clerk.

284
00:20:31,566 --> 00:20:33,376
Song Jiang.

285
00:20:34,205 --> 00:20:37,440
Traveling this nation, I had simply assumed

286
00:20:37,440 --> 00:20:43,620
officials and their pups
required incentive to do good.

287
00:20:44,650 --> 00:20:46,410
And you are?

288
00:20:47,545 --> 00:20:49,650
Right, my apologies.

289
00:20:49,650 --> 00:20:52,810
I am named Yang Zhi.

290
00:20:52,810 --> 00:20:59,550
I have never met an envoy
who did not demand bribery, either.

291
00:21:07,400 --> 00:21:09,870
Let our paths cross again.

292
00:21:17,370 --> 00:21:19,000
Song Jiang.

293
00:21:22,241 --> 00:21:24,070
Lu Zhi Shen, what brings you here?

294
00:21:24,070 --> 00:21:26,496
Chao Gai awaits your company.

295
00:21:26,496 --> 00:21:28,206
Understood.

296
00:21:34,915 --> 00:21:39,020
You seem jovial. Why is that?

297
00:21:39,020 --> 00:21:42,190
I met a rather interesting fellow.

298
00:21:42,190 --> 00:21:44,510
A refreshing man indeed.

299
00:21:44,510 --> 00:21:45,620
Have you fallen for him?

300
00:21:45,620 --> 00:21:48,370
- Is that so wrong?
- Not at all.

301
00:21:48,370 --> 00:21:52,475
You excel at seeing the good in people.

302
00:21:52,475 --> 00:21:54,475
As do you, old friend.

303
00:21:56,065 --> 00:22:01,360
Meeting new people
is truly a mysterious thing.

304
00:22:01,360 --> 00:22:06,670
Chao Gai, for example,
fills in for what I am missing.

305
00:22:06,670 --> 00:22:08,440
You are two hearts, beating as one.

306
00:22:08,440 --> 00:22:12,230
Of course, we still have our differences.

307
00:22:12,230 --> 00:22:16,128
Yet our goals are, miraculously,
one and the same.

308
00:22:16,128 --> 00:22:23,028
How will Chao Gai change this rotten country?

309
00:22:25,036 --> 00:22:28,376
He will have the citizens revolt,
and overthrow our government.

310
00:22:29,455 --> 00:22:33,070
If they can find just one fault
in our current regime,

311
00:22:33,070 --> 00:22:37,980
their rebellion will spread like wildfire.

312
00:22:37,980 --> 00:22:42,835
To make a country,
one must centralize that flame,

313
00:22:42,835 --> 00:22:48,435
to then burn down the old,
and make way for the new.

314
00:22:51,545 --> 00:22:54,806
Is that so strange a sentiment to make?

315
00:22:58,210 --> 00:23:01,170
- Or perhaps you are hungry?
- That, I am.

316
00:23:06,295 --> 00:23:12,910
[Shi Qian, Zhu Tong]

317
00:23:12,910 --> 00:23:16,360
Might I ask what those are?
[Lin Chong]

318
00:23:17,245 --> 00:23:21,940
Tags. Lin Chong's helps me feel his presence.

319
00:23:21,940 --> 00:23:27,540
Thus I decided to immortalize
our other comrades as well.

320
00:23:28,560 --> 00:23:33,370
Though our numbers are small,
we are not alone.

321
00:23:34,245 --> 00:23:37,287
I hope to meet them all soon.

322
00:23:38,385 --> 00:23:41,480
Zhu Tong and Lei Heng are soldiers.

323
00:23:41,480 --> 00:23:44,730
They protect Song Jiang from the shadows.

324
00:23:44,730 --> 00:23:49,090
Wu Song wanders the land,
searching for more comrades like myself.

325
00:23:49,090 --> 00:23:53,940
Ma Gui works as a spy, and gathers intel.

326
00:23:53,940 --> 00:23:57,230
Shi Qian is a fellow spy.

327
00:23:57,230 --> 00:23:59,585
While Dai Zong is a courier.

328
00:23:59,585 --> 00:24:02,560
I will introduce you to them all in due time.

329
00:24:02,560 --> 00:24:08,870
You treat those tags
as though they are treasures.

330
00:24:13,625 --> 00:24:15,520
Right.

331
00:24:15,520 --> 00:24:21,250
Someone may have caught wind
of our Salt Roads.

332
00:24:21,990 --> 00:24:24,170
- Lu Jun Yi.
- Yes, sir.

333
00:24:24,875 --> 00:24:28,560
Though the Salt Road is a complex system,
[Lu Jun Yi, Distributor of Salt]

334
00:24:28,560 --> 00:24:33,280
one of our many pathways
was nearly discovered.

335
00:24:33,280 --> 00:24:36,825
It is only thanks to Wu Yong's premonition

336
00:24:36,825 --> 00:24:39,503
that we avoided any danger.

337
00:24:40,250 --> 00:24:42,200
<i>He predicted we ought to close the route.</i>

338
00:24:48,745 --> 00:24:55,400
A sharp official amongst the fools
must have noticed our presence.

339
00:24:55,400 --> 00:24:56,829
<i>Indeed.</i>

340
00:24:56,829 --> 00:25:02,350
<i>When I am in Kaifeng,
I feel as though I am being observed.</i>

341
00:25:02,350 --> 00:25:08,400
What sort of official comes to mind?

342
00:25:08,400 --> 00:25:11,715
Lin Chong had made note of one.

343
00:25:11,715 --> 00:25:14,555
A suspicious man, named Li Fu.

344
00:25:15,745 --> 00:25:17,490
Li Fu.

345
00:25:17,490 --> 00:25:21,810
Song Jiang, can you use your network
to look into this man?

346
00:25:21,810 --> 00:25:24,425
I will have Ma Gui investigate him.

347
00:25:24,425 --> 00:25:28,775
Ma Gui alone will not suffice, no?

348
00:25:29,625 --> 00:25:34,770
I hear she was nearly found in Kaifeng,
and led one of her allies to death.

349
00:25:34,770 --> 00:25:38,430
Perhaps she is not suited to be a spy.

350
00:25:40,310 --> 00:25:42,850
Then I shall ask Shi Qian as well.

351
00:25:43,656 --> 00:25:47,796
He is a spy I can confidently send anywhere.

352
00:25:48,610 --> 00:25:50,080
Excellent.

353
00:25:51,325 --> 00:25:56,510
However, if our Salt Road is compromised,

354
00:25:56,510 --> 00:25:59,030
that would be the end for us.

355
00:25:59,030 --> 00:26:00,350
How do we combat this?

356
00:26:00,350 --> 00:26:02,690
Let us lead our enemies astray.

357
00:26:02,690 --> 00:26:07,425
Though they know of our presence,
they do not know our numbers.

358
00:26:07,425 --> 00:26:10,373
This is to our advantage.

359
00:26:10,373 --> 00:26:13,273
We will rob the country of its salt.

360
00:26:13,985 --> 00:26:15,280
Rob the country?

361
00:26:15,280 --> 00:26:17,830
I have already sent Ruan Xiao Wu
to the treasury.

362
00:26:17,830 --> 00:26:21,150
They will steal bags of salt,

363
00:26:21,150 --> 00:26:24,440
only for it to disappear without a trace.

364
00:26:24,440 --> 00:26:27,650
What a wasteful plan.

365
00:26:27,650 --> 00:26:30,310
Do they realize how heavy these bags are?

366
00:26:30,310 --> 00:26:36,350
I am more bothered
by this excessively villainous garb.

367
00:26:36,350 --> 00:26:41,600
We play the part of a fake gang of bandits,
the "Shadow Thieves".

368
00:26:41,600 --> 00:26:46,085
Let our enemies chase an illusion
for a while.

369
00:26:46,085 --> 00:26:49,035
"Disappear"? How?

370
00:26:50,860 --> 00:26:53,600
Where will we hide all the salt?

371
00:26:55,665 --> 00:26:57,560
We will not hide it.

372
00:26:57,560 --> 00:26:59,250
We will get rid of it.

373
00:27:00,060 --> 00:27:04,870
The sea will simply regain what it has lost.

374
00:27:10,885 --> 00:27:13,910
This is the most wasteful thing I've done.

375
00:27:13,910 --> 00:27:16,370
Less talking, more pouring.

376
00:27:16,370 --> 00:27:18,305
- Ready, and...
- Good.

377
00:27:18,305 --> 00:27:22,015
- Keep it up.
- This feels utterly wrong.

378
00:27:28,415 --> 00:27:30,280
7,000 granules, lost?

379
00:27:30,280 --> 00:27:31,900
Yes. They've disappeared without a trace.

380
00:27:31,900 --> 00:27:35,650
We may be dealing with a larger ensemble
than we first assumed.

381
00:27:35,650 --> 00:27:37,270
What else have you learned?

382
00:27:37,270 --> 00:27:39,400
The band calls themselves
the "Shadow Thieves".

383
00:27:39,400 --> 00:27:42,425
The citizens rally with them
as chivalrous bandits,

384
00:27:42,425 --> 00:27:44,445
as they have stolen from the country.

385
00:27:45,635 --> 00:27:48,350
Chivalry, as bandits?

386
00:27:48,350 --> 00:27:50,225
Continue to look into their whereabouts.

387
00:27:50,225 --> 00:27:51,605
Yes, sir.

388
00:28:02,480 --> 00:28:04,790
A larger ensemble, or so they claim.

389
00:28:07,447 --> 00:28:11,387
Never have we heard
of these "Shadow Thieves".

390
00:28:13,280 --> 00:28:18,970
How did this salt disappear under our watch?

391
00:28:21,900 --> 00:28:25,200
Nothing is adding up.

392
00:28:29,366 --> 00:28:32,796
A bad feeling such as this,

393
00:28:35,100 --> 00:28:37,760
is usually on the mark.

394
00:28:39,015 --> 00:28:40,920
- Li Fu.
- Sir?

395
00:28:40,920 --> 00:28:43,370
Raise the price of salt across the nation.
[Yuan Ming, Leader of Qinglian Temple]

396
00:28:43,370 --> 00:28:44,980
Immediately.

397
00:28:44,980 --> 00:28:46,135
Raise the price?

398
00:28:46,135 --> 00:28:50,395
We shall drag those chivalrous thieves
through the mud.

399
00:28:54,970 --> 00:28:58,950
[Notice: The price of salt will rise]

400
00:29:00,725 --> 00:29:02,650
They've outdone us.

401
00:29:02,650 --> 00:29:06,740
The Shadow Thieves are now
an enemy of the people.

402
00:29:06,740 --> 00:29:10,060
To think they could change
the market price of salt.

403
00:29:10,060 --> 00:29:12,000
This is unprecedented.

404
00:29:12,000 --> 00:29:17,650
I cannot think of anyone in Kaifeng
who can influence the price so quickly.

405
00:29:17,650 --> 00:29:20,011
What do you think, Wu Yong?

406
00:29:20,011 --> 00:29:22,281
I agree with Song Jiang.

407
00:29:23,805 --> 00:29:28,100
Regardless, now we can be certain.

408
00:29:28,100 --> 00:29:31,550
This invisible enemy
is aware of our presence.

409
00:29:48,185 --> 00:29:49,530
Sir! Sir!

410
00:29:49,530 --> 00:29:51,045
What?

411
00:29:51,045 --> 00:29:52,815
Give me a hand.

412
00:29:56,160 --> 00:29:57,580
Thank you.

413
00:30:01,552 --> 00:30:07,730
Do you truly plan to break An Dao Quan free?

414
00:30:07,730 --> 00:30:10,350
If he would allow himself to be, yes.

415
00:30:10,350 --> 00:30:13,655
You stand out.
You'll never be able to escape.

416
00:30:13,655 --> 00:30:16,065
I'm already a dead man.

417
00:30:17,440 --> 00:30:19,370
Escaping would be trivial.

418
00:30:20,151 --> 00:30:23,850
Take a look around this area.

419
00:30:23,850 --> 00:30:25,220
What?

420
00:30:28,250 --> 00:30:32,420
Every guard has his eyes on you.

421
00:30:34,845 --> 00:30:37,140
Now that you mention it.

422
00:30:37,140 --> 00:30:39,430
Help me carry this, would you?

423
00:30:44,200 --> 00:30:48,250
You're known as the Panther Head, aren't you?

424
00:30:51,305 --> 00:30:55,520
To think that nickname
would spread even here.

425
00:30:55,520 --> 00:30:58,940
You're also a former instructor
for the Imperial Guard.

426
00:30:58,940 --> 00:31:00,900
All the guards fear you,

427
00:31:00,900 --> 00:31:04,390
Panther Head, Lin Chong.

428
00:31:04,390 --> 00:31:05,590
I see.

429
00:31:05,590 --> 00:31:07,880
Ouch...

430
00:31:07,880 --> 00:31:10,020
Hey.

431
00:31:10,020 --> 00:31:11,135
Are you alright?

432
00:31:11,135 --> 00:31:14,775
I'm fine. Just my stomach.

433
00:31:15,533 --> 00:31:16,823
Say.

434
00:31:17,935 --> 00:31:21,200
If you take me along,

435
00:31:21,200 --> 00:31:24,120
I'll convince An Dao Quan to leave.

436
00:31:24,805 --> 00:31:28,100
I thought I will never be able to escape?

437
00:31:28,100 --> 00:31:29,993
Come visit An Dao Quan later.

438
00:31:29,993 --> 00:31:32,226
I'll explain the plan then.

439
00:31:32,226 --> 00:31:34,896
Hey, what are you two doing?

440
00:31:39,040 --> 00:31:40,830
My deepest apologies.

441
00:31:45,810 --> 00:31:47,840
Get back to work.

442
00:31:53,235 --> 00:31:57,190
Sir, you can't be standing out like that!

443
00:31:57,190 --> 00:31:58,950
Sorry.

444
00:31:58,950 --> 00:32:02,790
One more thing.
Be especially wary of those two.

445
00:32:06,585 --> 00:32:09,094
My hunch as a thief is telling me

446
00:32:09,094 --> 00:32:12,210
those two aren't like the other prisoners.

447
00:32:12,210 --> 00:32:16,040
They never take their eyes off you.

448
00:32:17,280 --> 00:32:18,640
I know.

449
00:32:26,645 --> 00:32:28,170
Where is Bai Sheng?

450
00:32:28,170 --> 00:32:29,770
What did you need from him?

451
00:32:29,770 --> 00:32:33,020
We planned to plot our escape.

452
00:32:33,020 --> 00:32:36,310
Bai Sheng is stealing a sharp tool
for me to use.

453
00:32:36,310 --> 00:32:37,890
He should return soon.

454
00:32:37,890 --> 00:32:42,730
And I will repeat,
I have no interest in escaping.

455
00:32:42,730 --> 00:32:45,085
Don't be so stubborn.

456
00:32:45,085 --> 00:32:48,552
Bai Sheng wants to break you free.

457
00:32:49,375 --> 00:32:52,054
I have returned.

458
00:32:52,054 --> 00:32:53,233
Bai Sheng.

459
00:32:53,233 --> 00:32:55,789
There you are.

460
00:32:58,110 --> 00:33:00,970
Now then, let's get down to business.

461
00:33:02,350 --> 00:33:04,540
Help me lift this.

462
00:33:06,040 --> 00:33:07,660
Heave-ho.

463
00:33:20,205 --> 00:33:21,850
Take a look.

464
00:33:21,850 --> 00:33:25,070
It's a map of this prison.

465
00:33:25,070 --> 00:33:26,600
How did you acquire this?

466
00:33:26,600 --> 00:33:29,335
I stole it, how else?

467
00:33:29,335 --> 00:33:34,065
Not even a rat
can sneak out of these walls.

468
00:33:35,005 --> 00:33:37,020
Then how do we escape?

469
00:33:37,020 --> 00:33:41,520
There may be no path for a rat,
but there is always a way for a thief.

470
00:33:41,520 --> 00:33:45,812
The unexpected route. That is our path.

471
00:33:46,845 --> 00:33:52,100
We will escape, like so.

472
00:33:52,100 --> 00:33:53,650
Are you a fool?

473
00:33:53,650 --> 00:33:55,440
That is right out the front gates.

474
00:33:55,440 --> 00:33:58,615
Exactly. You will shout it out,
loud and proud,

475
00:33:58,615 --> 00:34:03,065
and slay your way out the front gates.

476
00:34:03,860 --> 00:34:06,080
Why shout my name?

477
00:34:06,845 --> 00:34:11,490
You don't understand how weaklings feel, sir.

478
00:34:11,490 --> 00:34:17,950
The guards will hear your name,
and cower in fear.

479
00:34:19,035 --> 00:34:25,160
No one here can best you
in a one-on-one fight.

480
00:34:25,160 --> 00:34:26,840
Ain't that right?

481
00:34:32,845 --> 00:34:35,190
I may very well die.

482
00:34:35,190 --> 00:34:37,010
What a thrill.

483
00:34:38,270 --> 00:34:41,380
You speak of your own death
with such excitement.

484
00:34:43,885 --> 00:34:45,600
You were listening?

485
00:34:45,600 --> 00:34:49,350
Why do you rush to death's arms?

486
00:34:49,350 --> 00:34:52,400
All people are fated to die.

487
00:34:52,400 --> 00:34:55,610
I am simply accepting that outcome.

488
00:34:55,610 --> 00:34:57,770
No.

489
00:34:57,770 --> 00:35:00,295
You are ill.

490
00:35:00,295 --> 00:35:03,195
You crave death at every moment.

491
00:35:11,230 --> 00:35:17,420
<i>Love does not need a reason, my dear.</i>

492
00:35:23,535 --> 00:35:25,856
Can I be cured?

493
00:35:25,856 --> 00:35:31,266
A wound of the heart can only be mended
by the one who afflicted it.

494
00:35:32,370 --> 00:35:34,670
Then I am beyond saving.

495
00:35:38,870 --> 00:35:40,750
She...

496
00:35:43,100 --> 00:35:45,040
has already died.

497
00:35:48,480 --> 00:35:51,160
You certainly have it rough.

498
00:35:55,110 --> 00:35:57,240
Bai Sheng, what's wrong?

499
00:36:00,190 --> 00:36:02,080
What are you doing?

500
00:36:02,885 --> 00:36:05,260
He has a sharp object!

501
00:36:05,260 --> 00:36:07,270
You thief.

502
00:36:07,270 --> 00:36:08,900
Apprehend him!

503
00:36:08,900 --> 00:36:10,620
Stand!

504
00:36:10,620 --> 00:36:13,770
Yes, take him away!

505
00:36:13,770 --> 00:36:15,175
Wait! Bai Sheng!

506
00:36:15,175 --> 00:36:18,825
- Silence!
- He needs to be treated!

507
00:36:23,335 --> 00:36:25,150
Master Wang Jin!

508
00:36:25,150 --> 00:36:27,795
Please, wait!

509
00:36:27,795 --> 00:36:30,565
You are being far too cruel.

510
00:36:31,745 --> 00:36:34,770
I have taught you all I know.

511
00:36:34,770 --> 00:36:39,400
The rest, you must learn on your own.

512
00:36:39,400 --> 00:36:42,255
I still wish to learn under you, Master.

513
00:36:42,255 --> 00:36:47,865
You cannot leave now.

514
00:36:50,355 --> 00:36:52,580
Master Wang Jin.

515
00:36:52,580 --> 00:36:55,160
I wish to travel alongside you.

516
00:36:56,650 --> 00:37:01,790
Is that what I taught you, Shi Jin?

517
00:37:03,125 --> 00:37:07,440
I taught you the importance of gratitude.

518
00:37:07,440 --> 00:37:11,910
Abandoning your father,
all to follow your Master.

519
00:37:11,910 --> 00:37:15,600
Is that your way of being filial?

520
00:37:25,240 --> 00:37:28,340
Please, leave me one last lesson
before you part.

521
00:37:32,210 --> 00:37:34,630
This is no farewell.

522
00:37:37,730 --> 00:37:41,910
I will be alive within you.

523
00:37:43,230 --> 00:37:45,410
I know it to be true.

524
00:37:51,995 --> 00:37:53,683
Excellent work.

525
00:37:56,440 --> 00:37:58,830
Do not ever forget that sound.

526
00:38:05,190 --> 00:38:06,710
Let us be off.

527
00:38:29,080 --> 00:38:33,420
Was this moment all a dream, Father?

528
00:38:34,650 --> 00:38:37,680
It certainly felt like one.

529
00:38:39,170 --> 00:38:45,670
But you have undoubtedly
grown into a strong man.

530
00:38:55,125 --> 00:38:57,080
Lin Chong, you're late.

531
00:38:57,080 --> 00:38:58,925
Where are the herbs?

532
00:38:58,925 --> 00:39:00,815
I have them here.

533
00:39:02,360 --> 00:39:03,950
There.

534
00:39:05,955 --> 00:39:09,560
Useless junk, again.

535
00:39:09,560 --> 00:39:11,631
Bai Sheng would have...

536
00:39:11,631 --> 00:39:14,821
I am no doctor, nor am I Bai Sheng.

537
00:39:16,275 --> 00:39:18,940
Your anger is becoming obvious, An Dao Quan.

538
00:39:18,940 --> 00:39:23,675
It is my fault Bai Sheng was sent
to the discipline chamber.

539
00:39:23,675 --> 00:39:27,645
I had him steal many things for me.

540
00:39:31,580 --> 00:39:34,040
We can only wait for his return.

541
00:39:36,580 --> 00:39:41,370
Bai Sheng has an infection
within his stomach.

542
00:39:42,650 --> 00:39:44,710
If it breaks through his tissue,

543
00:39:45,987 --> 00:39:51,177
the infection will spread,
and kill Bai Sheng.

544
00:39:53,660 --> 00:39:58,410
Why do you obsess over Bai Sheng?

545
00:39:59,125 --> 00:40:01,520
I do not know.

546
00:40:01,520 --> 00:40:09,509
But I hate to imagine him in pain.

547
00:40:09,509 --> 00:40:13,869
Then he is your friend?

548
00:40:17,230 --> 00:40:20,380
I have never had a friend.

549
00:40:22,520 --> 00:40:25,420
Nor do I know what it means to be a friend.

550
00:40:26,980 --> 00:40:31,620
I simply cannot help but worry for Bai Sheng.

551
00:40:36,480 --> 00:40:40,510
That is because he is a friend, An Dao Quan.

552
00:40:42,290 --> 00:40:46,000
I, too, have my share of friends.

553
00:40:48,125 --> 00:40:50,270
This is a prison.

554
00:40:50,270 --> 00:40:52,840
All transactions are to be a trade.

555
00:40:54,585 --> 00:40:59,510
If I save your friend, Bai Sheng,

556
00:40:59,510 --> 00:41:02,480
will you come and save mine?

557
00:41:02,480 --> 00:41:04,790
Save Bai Sheng?

558
00:41:05,650 --> 00:41:07,370
How?

559
00:41:11,140 --> 00:41:13,000
We will escape.

560
00:41:36,200 --> 00:41:38,950
Hey! What are you doing?

561
00:41:40,080 --> 00:41:41,930
Lin Chong!

562
00:41:53,945 --> 00:41:56,460
<i>You will shout it out, loud and proud,</i>

563
00:41:56,460 --> 00:42:00,910
<i>and slay your way out the front gates.</i>

564
00:42:02,060 --> 00:42:06,210
<i>Perhaps it is time Lin Chong revives.</i>

565
00:42:10,165 --> 00:42:12,230
I, Lin Chong the Panther Head,

566
00:42:12,230 --> 00:42:14,700
will now be breaking free!

567
00:42:46,166 --> 00:42:48,056
Bai Sheng!

568
00:42:58,490 --> 00:43:00,210
Bai Sheng!

569
00:43:02,625 --> 00:43:04,070
This is no good.

570
00:43:04,070 --> 00:43:05,420
I must treat you.

571
00:43:05,420 --> 00:43:08,555
Start with the chains, they hurt.

572
00:43:08,555 --> 00:43:10,865
How can a thief not escape some chains?

573
00:43:20,335 --> 00:43:22,530
Can you stand?

574
00:43:22,530 --> 00:43:24,130
We have to go.

575
00:43:35,500 --> 00:43:38,010
Found them!

576
00:44:04,895 --> 00:44:08,620
Your movements tell me
you're no ordinary soldiers.

577
00:44:08,620 --> 00:44:10,375
Allow me a guess.

578
00:44:10,375 --> 00:44:13,685
Assassins hired by Gao Qiu?

579
00:45:03,196 --> 00:45:07,546
Let your bodies rot within the fodder.

580
00:45:34,400 --> 00:45:35,960
Sir!

581
00:45:40,786 --> 00:45:42,966
Are you alright, Bai Sheng?

582
00:45:57,600 --> 00:45:59,810
I'm sorry, Bai Sheng.

583
00:46:00,857 --> 00:46:03,417
Bai Sheng, pull through!

584
00:46:15,420 --> 00:46:19,750
[Lin Chong]

585
00:46:33,490 --> 00:46:35,200
Lin Chong...

586
00:46:41,030 --> 00:46:42,870
Are you alright?

587
00:46:43,816 --> 00:46:46,935
Bai Sheng, stay with us.

588
00:46:55,860 --> 00:46:57,660
Bai Sheng, stay steady!

589
00:47:00,770 --> 00:47:02,450
Lin Chong!

590
00:47:03,175 --> 00:47:05,570
Bai Sheng is at his limit.

591
00:47:05,570 --> 00:47:08,040
I must operate on him here.

592
00:47:09,480 --> 00:47:11,635
What?

593
00:47:11,635 --> 00:47:14,170
You are attempting the impossible.

594
00:47:14,170 --> 00:47:15,790
Bai Sheng.

595
00:47:17,379 --> 00:47:19,730
Bai Sheng, we will operate here.

596
00:47:19,730 --> 00:47:21,215
Hurry.

597
00:47:21,215 --> 00:47:23,177
Wait...

598
00:47:23,177 --> 00:47:26,707
Leave me behind.

599
00:47:28,035 --> 00:47:30,810
Do you know what I despise most of all?

600
00:47:30,810 --> 00:47:33,450
It is people who die without my permission.

601
00:47:34,270 --> 00:47:38,870
I will fight alongside you. So fight!

602
00:47:42,080 --> 00:47:43,830
Show me your stomach.

603
00:47:50,855 --> 00:47:52,690
Lin Chong, Bai Sheng will start flailing.

604
00:47:52,690 --> 00:47:54,540
Hold him down.

605
00:48:11,345 --> 00:48:13,240
You must live!

606
00:48:13,240 --> 00:48:15,375
I will escort you to safety.

607
00:48:15,375 --> 00:48:17,745
I will take you to my comrades!

608
00:48:29,825 --> 00:48:32,740
<i>Song Jiang did not evacuate from Yuncheng.</i>

609
00:48:32,740 --> 00:48:37,060
<i>He said he could not preach a great cause,</i>

610
00:48:37,060 --> 00:48:38,565
<i>if he did not even trust his own men.</i>

611
00:48:38,565 --> 00:48:42,565
<i>I will choose to believe in Lin Chong.</i>

612
00:48:45,980 --> 00:48:48,830
You must come out of this alive!

613
00:48:51,285 --> 00:48:54,490
Bai Sheng! Live!

614
00:48:54,490 --> 00:48:56,395
Bai Sheng!

615
00:48:56,395 --> 00:48:59,835
Bai Sheng!

616
00:50:00,810 --> 00:50:03,880
Lin Chong has broken out of prison.

617
00:51:05,940 --> 00:51:07,790
Song Jiang.

618
00:51:10,270 --> 00:51:12,210
How long will you stand there?

619
00:51:22,690 --> 00:51:24,330
I will join you.

620
00:51:52,370 --> 00:51:54,040
Sir Song Jiang!

621
00:51:57,600 --> 00:51:59,330
Song Jiang!

622
00:52:13,780 --> 00:52:15,500
Lin Chong?

623
00:52:30,940 --> 00:52:32,750
Lin Chong!

624
00:52:43,070 --> 00:52:44,990
Lin Chong!

625
00:52:58,580 --> 00:53:00,580
Lin Chong!

626
00:53:08,035 --> 00:53:10,240
Lin Chong!

627
00:53:10,240 --> 00:53:11,910
Lin Chong!

628
00:53:18,600 --> 00:53:20,300
An Dao Quan...

629
00:53:27,820 --> 00:53:31,400
[Lin Chong]

630
00:53:35,060 --> 00:53:36,760
Lin Chong!

631
00:53:46,985 --> 00:53:48,990
- An Dao Quan...
- Are you alright?

632
00:53:48,990 --> 00:53:50,600
Hey, are you alright?

633
00:53:50,600 --> 00:53:52,295
- Stay with us!
- Wake up.

634
00:53:52,295 --> 00:53:53,855
Wake up, I say!

635
00:54:01,140 --> 00:54:03,130
Lin Chong...

636
00:54:06,190 --> 00:54:08,180
has returned.

637
00:54:24,420 --> 00:54:26,580
Welcome home, Lin Chong.

638
00:55:06,414 --> 00:55:09,794
If he feels misplaced in the Imperial Guard,

639
00:55:09,794 --> 00:55:11,560
then I would like him for myself.

640
00:55:11,560 --> 00:55:13,850
Song Jiang is no ordinary clerk.

641
00:55:13,850 --> 00:55:16,600
Will you create a moment
for them to smile?

642
00:55:16,600 --> 00:55:18,600
I wish to have a lethal brigade.

643
00:55:18,600 --> 00:55:21,730
One that chooses to fight as a group.

644
00:55:21,730 --> 00:55:23,770
It is an impenetrable fortress.

645
00:55:23,770 --> 00:55:25,860
We cannot break in from the front gates.

646
00:55:25,860 --> 00:55:28,440
A monster resides within that fortress.

647
00:55:28,440 --> 00:55:30,190
A monster, known as "authority".

648
00:55:30,190 --> 00:55:34,030
A spy like myself
could never become a normal woman.

649
00:55:34,030 --> 00:55:38,100
Some suspicious civil officials
work under Cai Jing.

650
00:55:38,100 --> 00:55:42,335
Li Fu. The man Lin Chong feared?

651
00:55:42,335 --> 00:55:45,975
Chao Gai, I want you to strike me down.

652
00:57:28,532 --> 00:57:34,312
[Episode 3 - FIN]

